high_descs: Go forward toward the trash bin, then turn right and go to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and go forward, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the pot inside, chill it, then take it out.
Turn right and move forward, then turn left to go to the white table.
Put the pot on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the white table

high_descs: Walk over to the silver can in front of you, then hang a right and walk over to the oven.
Pick up the metal pan off of the front right burner of the stove.
Walk over to the black fridge behind you.
Open the fridge and put the pan inside on the top shelf then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up then take out the pan and close the fridge.
Walk over to the small white table behind you.
Put the cold metal pan on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold metal pan on a white table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the stove across the room.
Pick up the pan on the front, right burner of the stove.
Turn around and go across the kitchen, to the refrigerator on the left.
Place the pan on the right of the top shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the pan from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the white table across from you.
Place the pan on the center of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the table.
